<HEADLINE>
<P>
NUCLEAR WEAPONS PORN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A July 12 article described the use of computers at the Lawrence Livermore 
National Laboratory "to store and distribute hard-core pornography." It is 
unfortunate that many Americans still have not recognized that the work of the 
nuclear weapons labs in designing, testing and improving nuclear weapons is an 
even more serious form of pornography. What could be more obscene than 
developing weapons that melt eyeballs, cook flesh and incinerate human beings 
-- weapons of mass murder that place the entire human species in danger of 
annihilation? 
</P>
<P>
 DAVID KRIEGER, President 
</P>
<P>
 Nuclear Age Peace Foundation 
</P>
<P>
 Santa Barbara 
</P>
