</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Comedy Central will air a two-hour telethon Tuesday to raise money for 
President Clinton's Legal Defense Fund. The fund-raiser will air with the Jerry 
Lewis film "The Bellboy" at 
</P>
<P>
 10 p.m. A network spokesman said: "We're hoping to collect as much as $40 -- 
or even $50." 
</P>
