<DOCID> 063800 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
July 25, 1994, Monday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Part F; Page 3; Column 4; Entertainment Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
