ORANGE COUNTY FOCUS: BREA; TOWN HALL MEETING SET FOR WEDNESDAY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By ALAN EYERLY 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The City Council will have a town hall meeting Wednesday to give residents an 
opportunity to discuss their concerns and suggestions with the elected 
officials. 
</P>
<P>
 This "Let's Talk Brea" informal gathering is scheduled for 7 p.m. at William 
E. Fanning Elementary School, 650 N. Apricot Ave. 
</P>
<P>
 The council had two town hall meetings earlier in the year at local schools. 
</P>
<P>
 For more information, call (714) 990-7600.ALAN EYERLY 
</P>
